    /**
    Writea  function thattake s a message, and encodes in such a
    waythat it  s waps caseof al l letters, replaces a llvowels in   the message  with the letter that appears 2 places ahea d of that
    vowel  in the  english alphabet.
   Ass ume onl y letters.

